    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-cc4cf4a2-ba7f-45b8-a3e9-a25eb0a2ac90">
                Mr. Mander
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-cc4cf4a2-ba7f-45b8-a3e9-a25eb0a2ac90" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1941-01-21/debates/d1a4ad8a-90c9-48c4-bb63-b8b7d4cf8b08/WarAndPeaceAims#contribution-cc4cf4a2-ba7f-45b8-a3e9-a25eb0a2ac90">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Prime Minister whether he is now able to make a statement with reference to the war and peace aims of the Government?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-cc4cf4a2-ba7f-45b8-a3e9-a25eb0a2ac90" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1941-01-21/debates/d1a4ad8a-90c9-48c4-bb63-b8b7d4cf8b08/WarAndPeaceAims#contribution-cc4cf4a2-ba7f-45b8-a3e9-a25eb0a2ac90">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-a9e1e2a6-e199-4206-88cc-f6dc3d5e0adb">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-a9e1e2a6-e199-4206-88cc-f6dc3d5e0adb">
