                Mr. Stephen
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-17e29e2f-927f-4fbb-a127-61bd73af6b45" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
