    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is the right hon. Gentleman not unduly optimistic about how well aware people in other countries are?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-17e29e2f-927f-4fbb-a127-61bd73af6b45" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
