    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Prime Minister whether, in the light of the situation in North Africa and the Mediterranean, he will consider definitely advising the Italian people of the peace aims of the <span id="23" class="column-number" data-column-number="23"></span> British Commonwealth in relation to their country, so that they may be under no misapprehension as to the purpose for which they are being called upon to fight?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
